ccarin In Final Talks To Join Gerard Butler In ‘Greenland’ Thriller At STX|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Amanda|last=N'Duka|date=2019-06-18|accessdate=2019-11-05|archive-date=2022-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220331154804/https://deadline.com/2019/06/morena-baccarin-gerard-butler-greenland-stx-1202634421/}}</ref>。2019年7月，[[史考特·葛倫|史考特·葛倫]]、{{le|金·巴赫|King Bach|安德魯·巴赫勒}}和羅傑·戴爾·弗洛伊德（{{lang|en|Roger Dale Floyd}}）確認參演<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/07/greenland-stx-gerard-butler-andrew-bachelor-scott-glenn-1202645663/|title=‘Greenland’: STX Gerard Butler-Led Thriller Adds Andrew Bachelor & Scott Glenn|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Amanda|last=N'Duka|date=2019-07-15|accessdate=2019-11-05|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225200337/https://deadline.com/2019/07/greenland-stx-gerard-butler-andrew-bachelor-scott-glenn-1202645663/}}</ref>。2019年8月，[[大衛·丹曼|大衛·丹曼]]也簽約出演<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/08/david-denman-gerard-butler-greenland-stx-1202669231/|title=David Denman Cast In STX’s ‘Greenland’ Thriller|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Amanda|last=N'Duka|date=2019-08-15|accessdate=2019-11-05|archive-date=2021-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210826001535/https://deadline.com/2019/08/david-denman-gerard-butler-greenland-stx-1202669231/}}</ref>。

