== 反響 ==
=== 評價 ===
電影評價兩極分化，但以肯定居多。評論匯總網站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據152條評論，新鮮度78％，平均評分為6.3／10；共識評論：「當心了，《天劫倒數》的彗星：傑瑞德·巴特勒在這裡保護地球，同時向觀眾展現了令人難以置信的娛樂體驗。」<ref>{{cite web|title=Greenland (2020)|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/greenland|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|access-date=2021-02-18|archive-date=2022-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220322090033/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/greenland}}</ref>在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，得分64，代表「普遍好評」<ref>{{cite web|title=Greenland Reviews|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/greenland|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|access-date=2021-02-25|archive-date=2022-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220314074101/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/greenland}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
《天劫倒數》最先於比利時全球首映，首週末在55間戲院中獲得7萬美元的票房<ref>{{Cite web |title= Belgian 2020 Weekend 31: July 29-August 2, 2020 |work= Box Office Mojo |url= https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/2020W31/?area=BE&ref_=bo_rl_table_1 |access-date= 2020-08-07 |archive-date= 2021-01-29 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210129235822/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/2020W31/?area=BE&ref_=bo_rl_table_1 }}</ref>。在法國上映的第一天，電影票房收入25.5萬美元，售出3.1萬張票；雖然戲院少加上COVID-19的嚴格管制，但仍比巴特勒的《[[全面攻佔：倒數救援|全面攻佔：倒數救援]]》（2013年）高出61%。它在該國的首映票房為109萬美元，並在全球於十天累積至130萬美元的票房<ref name=FranceOpening>{{Cite news |last=Tartaglione |first=Nancy |title=‘1917’ Leads China Weekend; Korea Has Yet Another Hit With ‘Deliver Us From Evil’ & ‘Greenland’ Makes Hay In France – International Box Office |language=en |work=Deadline Hollywood |url=https://deadline.com/2020/08/china-1917-interstellar-dolittle-ford-v-ferrari-greenland-international-box-office-1203007208/ |date=2020-08-09 |access-date=2020-08-09 |archive-date=2021-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218155705/https://deadline.com/2020/08/china-1917-interstellar-dolittle-ford-v-ferrari-greenland-international-box-office-1203007208/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Budget>{{Cite news |last= Moreau |first= Jordan |title= Box Office: Shia LaBeouf’s ‘The Tax Collector’ Takes In $317,000 |language= en |work= Variety |url= https://variety.com/2020/film/box-office/the-tax-collector-shia-labeouf-box-office-1234729945/ |date= 2020-08-09 |access-date= 2020-08-09 |archive-date= 2021-02-18 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210218155647/https://variety.com/2020/film/box-office/the-tax-collector-shia-labeouf-box-office-1234729945/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。在國際發行的第三個週末，《天劫倒數》在九個地區並取得2.82萬美元的票房<ref>{{Cite news |last=Tartaglione |first=Nancy |title=‘Harry Potter And The Sorcerer’s Stone’ Nears $1B WW With Magical China Reissue – International Box Office |language=en |work=Deadline Hollywood |url=https://deadline.com/2020/08/china-harry-potter-eight-hundred-interstellar-bad-boys-for-life-inception-international-box-office-coronavirus-1203013370/ |date=2020-08-16 |access-date=2020-08-16 |archive-date=2020-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819073429/https://deadline.com/2020/08/china-harry-potter-eight-hundred-interstellar-bad-boys-for-life-inception-international-box-office-coronavirus-1203013370/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 續集 ==
2021年6月，據報導，電影將開發續集《天劫倒數2：遷移》（{{lang|en|''Greenland: Migration''}}），劇情將圍繞蓋瑞提穿越冰凍的歐洲荒地尋找新家園的旅程展開；導演沃和演員巴特勒、芭卡琳與弗洛伊德都將回歸。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Barraclough|first=Leo|last2=Barraclough|first2=Leo|date=2021-06-14|title=Gerard Butler, Morena Baccarin to Reprise Roles in ‘Greenland’ Sequel|url=https://variety.com/2021/film/global/gerard-butler-morena-baccarin-greenland-1234995827/|access-date=2021-06-15|website=Variety|archive-date=2021-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210710091354/https://variety.com/2021/film/global/gerard-butler-morena-baccarin-greenland-1234995827/|dead-url=no}}</ref>次月，STX以7500萬美元的價格在[[第74屆坎城影展|第74屆坎城影展]]上取得該片的全球發行權<ref>{{Cite web|last=Wiseman|first=Andreas|last2=Wiseman|first2=Andreas|date=2021-07-06|title=‘Greenland’ Sequel ‘Migration’ Sells To STX In Massive $75M+ Deal At Cannes Virtual Market|url=https://deadline.com/2021/07/gerard-butler-greenland-sequel-migration-sells-stx-cannes-market-deal-1234784916/|access-date=2021-07-07|website=Deadline|archive-date=2021-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210711041357/https://deadline.com/2021/07/gerard-butler-greenland-sequel-migration-sells-stx-cannes-market-deal-1234784916/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並同意為續集提供6500萬美元的預算<ref name="Deadline(2021-07-06)">{{cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2021/07/gerard-butler-greenland-sequel-migration-sells-stx-cannes-market-deal-1234784916/|title=‘Greenland’ Sequel ‘Migration’ Sells To STX In Massive $75M+ Deal At Cannes Virtual Market|last=Wiseman|first=Andreas|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2021-07-06|accessdate=2021-07-08|archive-date=2021-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210711041357/https://deadline.com/2021/07/gerard-butler-greenland-sequel-migration-sells-stx-cannes-market-deal-1234784916/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

